            However, in the heat and burden of this Bill, far be it from me to labour to protect the Charity Commission from its powers. I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.</p><p>
            Amendment, by leave, withdrawn.</p><p>
            Clause 24 agreed to.</p><p>
            Clause 25 agreed to.</p><p>
            Clause 26 <span class="italic">[Power to enter premises and seize documents etc.]:</span>
          </p>
