      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0670P0-04906'>
        <a name='S5LV0670P0_20050314_GCR_125'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-bassam' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0670P0_20050314_GCR_125' title='Link to this speech by Mr John Bassam' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
